{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841239605,"sessionID":"ses_2879e34cfffeVEXMbQEUVmsl00","part":{"id":"prt_d7862e20f0016fbd6DYyWGi203","messageID":"msg_d786257dd0013G1PH9ORph4abj","sessionID":"ses_2879e34cfffeVEXMbQEUVmsl00","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-b0e9aaa7a9104d948e50605442687e5f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `pkg/apis`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: S\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Create constants.go file\n- [ ] Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants.go`\n- [ ] Define default timeout constants\n  - [ ] `DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout` = 5 minutes\n  - [ ] `SessionTimeoutDefault` = 15 minutes\n  - [ ] `MaxSessionDurationDefault` = 8 hours\n- [ ] Define runtime type constants\n  - [ ] `RuntimeTypePython` = \"python\"\n  - [ ] `RuntimeTypeJavaScript` = \"javascript\"\n  - [ ] `RuntimeTypeTypeScript` = \"typescript\"\n  - [ ] `RuntimeTypeGo` = \"go\"\n- [ ] Define protocol type constants\n  - [ ] `ProtocolTCP` = \"TCP\"\n  - [ ] `ProtocolUDP` = \"UDP\"\n  - [ ] `ProtocolSCTP` = \"SCTP\"\n- [ ] Define default resource limit constants\n  - [ ] `DefaultCPULimit` = \"1\"\n  - [ ] `DefaultMemoryLimit` = \"1Gi\"\n  - [ ] `DefaultCPURequest` = \"100m\"\n  - [ ] `DefaultMemoryRequest` = \"128Mi\"\n- [ ] Define seccomp profile type constants\n  - [ ] `SeccompProfileTypeRuntimeDefault` = \"RuntimeDefault\"\n  - [ ] `SeccompProfileTypeUnconfined` = \"Unconfined\"\n  - [ ] `SeccompProfileTypeLocalhost` = \"Localhost\"\n- [ ] Verify constants.go compiles without errors\n- [ ] Verify all constants are exported (public)\n\n**Verification**: Run `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` to ensure the file compiles\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: Update types.go to reference constants\n- [ ] Update `types.go` to reference constants where appropriate\n  - [ ] Review AgentRuntimeSpec default values documentation\n  - [ ] Review CodeInterpreterSpec default values documentation\n  - [ ] Review SandboxContainerPort default protocol documentation\n  - [ ] Review SandboxSeccompProfile documentation\n- [ ] Ensure no hardcoded string literals for runtime types\n- [ ] Ensure no hardcoded string literals for protocol types\n- [ ] Ensure no hardcoded string literals for seccomp profile types\n- [ ] Verify all CRD validation tags reference correct constants\n- [ ] Verify all kubebuilder default tags match constants\n\n**Verification**: Run `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` and review types.go for hardcoded literals\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Create constants_test.go\n- [ ] Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants_test.go`\n- [ ] Add test for default timeout constants\n  - [ ] `TestDefaultCodeExecutionTimeout`\n  - [ ] `TestSessionTimeoutDefault`\n  - [ ] `TestMaxSessionDurationDefault`\n- [ ] Add test for runtime type constants\n  - [ ] `TestRuntimeTypes` - verify all runtime types are non-empty\n  - [ ] `TestRuntimeTypesUnique` - verify runtime types are unique\n- [ ] Add test for protocol type constants\n  - [ ] `TestProtocolTypes` - verify all protocol types are non-empty\n  - [ ] `TestProtocolTypesUnique` - verify protocol types are unique\n- [ ] Add test for resource limit constants\n  - [ ] `TestDefaultCPULimit`\n  - [ ] `TestDefaultMemoryLimit`\n  - [ ] `TestDefaultCPURequest`\n  - [ ] `TestDefaultMemoryRequest`\n- [ ] Add test for seccomp profile type constants\n  - [ ] `TestSeccompProfileTypes` - verify all profile types are non-empty\n  - [ ] `TestSeccompProfileTypesUnique` - verify profile types are unique\n\n**Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 -run TestDefaultCodeExecutionTimeout` and all constant tests\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Add validation helper functions (optional but recommended)\n- [ ] Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/validation.go`\n- [ ] Add `ValidateRuntimeType(runtime string) error` function\n  - [ ] Check if runtime type matches one of the defined constants\n  - [ ] Return descri